``It's A Wonderful Job,'' episode of ``Moonlighting,'' ABC; Georgia
Jeffries, ``Turn, Turn, Turn, Part I,'' episode of ``Cagney &
Lacey,'' CBS.
   Episodic comedy (three-way tie): Barry Fanaro and Mort Nathan,
``'Twas the Nightmare Before Christmas,'' episode of ``The Golden
Girls,'' NBC; Gary David Goldberg and Alan Uger, ``A, My Name is
Alex, Part II,'' episode of ``Family Ties,'' NBC; Jay Tarses,
