its offer after studying non-public information provided by the Los
Angeles-based company that has about 1,000 printing centers
franchised in the United States, Canada and the United Kingdom.
   Last year, PIP escaped a hostile bid by Tarrytown, N.Y.-based
Kane-Miller Corp.
